snippet.title: 2023's First SM64 Hack LZJ's Galaxy Trip Release! Also the third Chinese hack
snippet.description:
After Slask's Adventure and Mario's Trip in China, this is the third SM64 hack from China, also 2023's first SM64 hack, and the authors is me, Liu Zijun!

I don't know if this hack will start a new era of hacking but I have confidence that you never seen many things in my hack before. See videos on youtube for those brilliant ideas! I strongly recommend you have a try of my hack.
 
After the trip of China, this trip is more thrilling, which is in the Galaxy. This time you will soar in the endless universe and visit many fantasty galaxies you've never seen before.  Wish you enjoy this trip!

Contact: 
My email: 84316326@163.com   zijunliu96@gmail.com
My youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYoNIigww6DAfxRlTtgrvFw
Discord: liuzijun#5957
If you find any bugs please tell me! Thanks a lot of that!
